{
  "stem": "1249.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, uh-huh.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she went, sorry, but she says she has to do it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was crying.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I didn't want to pull up my [SOBS] skirt.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] And the general said to me, if you are not going to pull up your skirt, and you won't let pull up your panty, I'm going to go in with my-- she had this terrible, big stick.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [SOBS] with that stick, and she stepped close to us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she had to examine us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the whole examination was-- they thought-- they were telling because maybe the Jude-- maybe the Jewish people [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] were putting some jewelry in, you know?",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How could they do for a young girl who was a virgin?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Not even go-- would not go out with a boy at this time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so rudely to us-- to us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Even the girl would-- would have been-- he was sym-- she was sympathetic.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But she had to do it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And oh.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't care how nicely you do it, or how careful you do it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You still a virgin.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And going in with your hand up, you know, it was a terrible feeling.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I have to tell you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I'm not a youngster anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "When I go to the gynecologist, she knows my story, this part of the story.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And she's the most generous lady, because she knows what I went through.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And, and she's very careful.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Otherwise, I was always terrified to go to a gynecologist since this time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was the Hungarians, the Hungarian police, and this professional--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The 'csendor,' the 'csendor.'",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, nothing.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was, again, just to, to torture the people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when I came out, the other people came to me.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
